txt.en: You have defeated many Sûhalar Easterlings.
You have defeated many Sûhalar Easterlings so that Ingold can remain at his watch over the North-gate.
Sûhalar Easterlings can be found in the northern section of Pelennor Fields.\n\nYou should defeat Sûhalar Easterlings so that Ingold can keep hold of the North-gate.
'These mysterious axe-wielding Easterlings from the north must be dealt with. Some have recently entered the Pelennor. Find them and defeat them before they gain even more ground.'
Ingold, captain of the Out-wall, keeps the North-gate of the Rammas clear of enemy forces. However, Sûhalar Easterlings from the north keep gaining ground in Pelennor Fields.
